name: Smart Text Chat
description: This AI model is designed to understand and generate human-like text. It's excellent for conversations, following instructions, and handling various text-based tasks. Best for engaging in text-based chats, writing, summarizing, coding, and solving math problems.

name: High-Precision Text AI
description: This is a more powerful version of Google's Gemma 3 model, offering higher accuracy for text-based tasks. It provides a deeper understanding of language. Best for advanced text understanding, detailed descriptions, and complex text reasoning.

name: Versatile Text AI
description: Google's Gemma2 model is a robust text-based AI that can handle diverse language tasks. It's designed for broad text comprehension and generation. Best for general text generation, understanding complex written information, and various conversational tasks.

name: Mobile Text Edge
description: This is a highly optimized version of the Gemma2 model, specifically designed to run efficiently on mobile and edge devices. It's compact and powerful for text processing. Best for fast text generation and understanding on devices with limited resources.

name: Ultimate Vision Assistant
description: This is Google's advanced AI model that truly shines at understanding both text and images. It can "see" what's in a picture and discuss it with you. Best for vision-language tasks like image analysis, creating descriptions for images, and answering questions about visuals.

name: Thinking & Reasoning Assistant
description: A distilled, lightweight version of DeepSeek-R1 designed to retain strong reasoning, chain-of-thought, and math-solving capabilities. Optimized for mobile and edge use, it excels in multi-step thinking tasks, structured reasoning, and logic-based question answering.
